#. type: table
#: original_texis/gettext.texi:1520
msgid "The @code{c-format} flag indicates that the untranslated string and the translation are supposed to be C format strings.  The @code{no-c-format} flag indicates that they are not C format strings, even though the untranslated string happens to look like a C format string (with @samp{%} directives)."
